<concept id="scanning_for_malware">
    <title>Scan for Virus and Malware</title>
    <shortdesc>Run manual scans to detect virus and other threats on your computer.</shortdesc>
    <conbody>
        <note type="important">
            <p conref="../conrefs_variables/notes_conref.xml#notes_conref/p_ms5_wgj_4vb"/>
        </note>
        <p><ph conkeyref="ClamWinVARS/short_product_name">product_name</ph> allows you to scan files and folders on your computer to detect threats such as virus and other malware. To keep your system clean, it is recommended to run scans regularly.</p>
        <p><ph conkeyref="ClamWinVARS/short_product_name">product_name</ph> offers the following types of scan.</p>
        <ul id="ul_dk4_vpj_4vb">
            <li>
                <p><xref href="full_system_scan.xml">Full system scan</xref></p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p><xref href="scan_files_folders.xml">Custom scan</xref></p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p><xref href="scan_memory_processes.xml">Computer memory scan</xref></p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p><xref href="scheduled_scan.xml">Scheduled scan</xref></p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </conbody>
</concept>
